@HttpFiles_HotAddress = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@IdCaballo = c4ccabe5-f359-4708-b1d8-029af994f25b
@IdVideo = xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

### ===============================
### VIDEOS - VENDEDOR
### ===============================

### Subir Video (URL de YouTube)

POST {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/horses/{{IdCaballo}}/videos
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="video_url"

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ejemplo123
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Listar Videos de un Caballo

GET {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/horses/{{IdCaballo}}/videos
Accept: application/json


### ===============================
### VIDEOS - ADMIN
### ===============================

### Listar todos los videos pendientes

GET {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/videos?status=pending
Accept: application/json

### Listar todos los videos verificados

GET {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/videos?status=verified
Accept: application/json

### Listar todos los videos rechazados

GET {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/videos?status=rejected
Accept: application/json

### Listar todos los videos (sin filtro)

GET {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/videos
Accept: application/json

### Ver detalle de un video

GET {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/videos/{{IdVideo}}
Accept: application/json

### Aprobar un video (verificar)

PATCH {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/videos/{{IdVideo}}/review
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "verified"
}

### Rechazar un video (con motivo obligatorio)
### Envía mensaje automático al vendedor vía chat

PATCH {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/videos/{{IdVideo}}/review
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "rejected",
  "reason": "El video no muestra claramente al caballo."
}
